<h1 class="page-title"></h1>
<div class="page-content">
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong>POLECAMY EKOGROSZEK </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong>SKARBEK I RETOPAL<br /></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><br /></span></strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><img title="SKARBEK LOGO" src="http://maratonkielce.pl/media_library/2016/11/24/147998100642.jpg" alt="SKARBEK LOGO" width="125" height="69" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></strong></span><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><img title="retopal" src="http://maratonkielce.pl/media_library/2015/1/13/142114713294.png" alt="retopal" width="172" height="51" /></span></strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><br /></span></strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px; font-family: andale mono,times;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #003366;"><span style="color: #003366;">Ekogroszek oryginalnie pakowany w kopalni.</span> Zar&oacute;wno Skarbek jak i Retopal powstaja z&nbsp;wyselekcjonowanych wegli o najlepszych parametrach. Wysoka jakosc pozwala na&nbsp;stosowanie tego paliwa w&nbsp;kotlach spelniajacych wszelkie wymagania ekologiczne. Dzieki dbalosci o jakosc paliwo to cechuje sie dynamicznie rosnaca popularnoscia wsr&oacute;d odbiorc&oacute;w krajowych.</span></span></strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><strong style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #003366;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times;"><strong>Posiadaja swiadectwo badania na "znak bezpieczenstwa ekologicznego".</strong></span><br /></span></span></strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a title="Ekogroszek" href="/pl/ekogroszek/">Parametry jakosciowe</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong>BETON KOM&Oacute;RKOWY</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;"><img style="float: left;" title="sbpaleta" src="http://maratonkielce.pl/media_library/2013/1/30/135954763032_200x170.jpg" alt="sbpaleta" width="200" height="170" /></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;">Bialy.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;">Wszystkie odmiany od 400 do 600.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;">Szerokosc muru od 5cm.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;">Powierzchnia gladka lub P+W.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;">Zapeniamy transport i rozladunek HDS.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;"><br /></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;"><br /></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; color: #ff6600; font-size: 31px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366; font-size: 17px;">Cena zalezna od ilosci i miejsca dostawy, dlatego w celu jej ustalenia prosimy o kontakt.<br /></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; font-size: 31px; color: #ff6600;"><span style="font-size: 6px;"><br /></span></span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; font-size: 31px; color: #ff6600;">PLYTA GIPS KARTON/WELNA MINERALNA <br /></span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img title="plyta GK" src="http://maratonkielce.pl/media_library/2010/10/1286448013_300x225.jpg" alt="plyta GK" width="254" height="191" /><img title="ursa DF" src="http://maratonkielce.pl/media_library/2013/11/26/138546221899_188x250.jpg" alt="ursa DF" width="188" height="250" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366;">Welna mineralna, wszystkie rodzaje i grubosci.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366;">Plyta gips karton biala i zielona wym. 1,2x2,6m<br /></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: andale mono,times; font-size: 17px;"><strong><span style="color: #003366;">W celu ustalenia cen prosimy o kontakt telefoniczny lub mailowy.</span></strong></span></p>
