<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="font-size: 17px;">MOZLIWOSC PRZECHOWANIA MATERIAL&Oacute;W BEZ DODATKOWYCH OPLAT!!!</span></strong></span></span></p>
